@node "Hints" "Hints"
@next "Bugs"
@prev "Tips"

If you haven't result when you run @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub}.


Perhaps PATH is badly set.


To find solution, look the temporary file created by @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub}.
It's named @{b}T:WHDAutoLaunch.script@{ub}.


@endnode

;***************************************
@node "Bugs" "Bugs"
@next "FAQ"
@prev "Hints"

-" various/" folder aren't supported, you must rename it as ".various".


- " " don't supported as first and last letter in the name of @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub}'s
    parameter.


- "+" symbol aren't supported too in the name of the @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub}'s
    parameter (Bubble+).

@endnode

