@node "FAQ" "FAQ"
@next "Greeting"
@prev "Bugs"

  Q: There aren't result when I run WHDAutoLaunch command
  A: Perhaps PATH isn't found then read @{"hints" link "Hints" 0} and @{"re-configure" link "Config" 0}

  Q:
  A:


@endnode

