;***************************************
@node "OpenFolder" "OpenFolder"

@{b}OpenFolder@{ub} option can be set at the third line of @{"WHDAutoLaunch.Prefs" link "Config" 0}


  If this Option is set in prefs file when @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub} command is executed,


  only folder of the demo/game will be opened but game will not launch.



 REMARK: if there aren't option set in Prefs file then @{b}@{"LaunchGame" link "LaunchGame" 0} & OpenFolder@{ub}
 options will be simultaneously activated

@endnode


;***************************************
@node "LaunchGame" "LaunchGame"


 @{b}LaunchGame@{ub} option can be set at the third line of @{"WHDAutoLaunch.Prefs" link "Config" 0}


  If this Option is set in prefs file when @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub} command is executed,


  game/demo will launch using WHDLoad's Slave but game/demo's Workench folder


  will not be opened.



 REMARK: if there aren't option set in prefs file then @{b}@{"OpenFolder" link "OpenFolder" 0} & LaunchGame@{ub}
 options will be simultaneously activated

@endnode

;***************************************
@node "Requester" "Requester"


 @{b}Requester@{ub} option can be set at the third line of @{"WHDAutoLaunch.Prefs" link "Config" 0}


 If this option is set in prefs file when @{b}WHDAutoLaunch@{ub} is executed,


 a requester will appear and will ask you what option you wish use @{"LaunchGame" link "LaunchGame" 0}


 or @{"OpenFolder" link "OpenFolder" 0}.


@endnode

